class.description:
PLATEAUCityModel is the primary class for loading PLATEAU CityGML files and extracting mesh data. It handles parsing of CityGML format, texture loading, and conversion to Godot-compatible meshes.
[codeblock]
var city_model = PLATEAUCityModel.new()
if city_model.load("path/to/file.gml"):
    var options = PLATEAUMeshExtractOptions.new()
    options.coordinate_zone_id = 9  # Tokyo
    var meshes = city_model.extract_meshes(options)
[/codeblock]
